1
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:46,220
=Episode 1=

2
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:48,680
(I once thought)

3
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,040
(I was going to lose her.)

4
00:00:52,320 --> 00:00:53,280
(So...)

5
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:55,520
(I left behind everything I owned,)

6
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,240
(including)

7
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,680
(my properties,)

8
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,800
(the Comic gallery,)

9
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,480
(and)

10
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,440
(its entire collection,)

11
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,880
(every bit of it,)

12
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:09,280
(to my daughter,)

13
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:11,840
(Qiao Xiaomi,)

14
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,360
(as her sole heir.)

15
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,920
We will always love you

16
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,640
and always miss you.

17
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:51,040
Thank you all for coming
to my dad's memorial service.

18
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,560
Let's take a look back

19
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,720
at the work he loved most in his life.

20
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,200
Mr. Qiao,

21
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,160
after that fire,

22
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,280
Miss Qiao may develop

23
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,240
post-traumatic stress disorder.

24
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,520
From now on, she should avoid

25
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,560
anything related to fire if possible.

26
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,520
Understood.

27
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,160
Thank you, Dr. Lin.

28
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:09,560
You old fool.

29
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,360
You left your entire fortune

30
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,200
to this useless idiot

31
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,040
who can't remember a thing.

32
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,800
Aren't you worried she won't
be able to handle it?

33
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,080
So,

34
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,080
my dear sister,

35
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,640
do you like the gift I got you?

36
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,200
Qiao Xiaomi!

37
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:36,080
Get away from me!

38
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,320
I'm sorry.

39
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,520
I'm late.

40
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,440
Who are you?

41
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:37,620
=Visage and Soul=

42
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,620
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

43
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,160
You're awake.

44
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,840
You just fainted.

45
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,160
Have some warm water.

46
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,120
Xiaomi.

47
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,000
Do you really not remember me?

48
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,600
I'm Qin Yu.

49
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,000
I've come back to marry you.

50
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,400
I'm your fiancé.

51
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,560
They all said you had amnesia.
I didn't believe them.

52
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,040
You're taking advantage of me.

53
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,520
Isn't the one taking advantage of you

54
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,160
your beloved brother,

55
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,080
Qiao Zhiwei?

56
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,200
For you,

57
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,040
I'd be your fire in the cold.

58
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,640
In this house,

59
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,640
no one is allowed to mention
anything related to fire.

60
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,680
I don't know you.

61
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,880
Leave now.

62
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:50,960
Stop right there.

63
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,160
A fiancé who suddenly showed up

64
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,920
out of nowhere.

65
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,160
The grand gift I carefully prepared

66
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,000
was completely ruined by you.

67
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,160
Qiao Zhiwei,

68
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,880
to hurt Xiaomi,

69
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,880
you'd even sabotage
your own father's funeral.

70
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,680
It's been three years.

71
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,440
How are you still such a loser?

72
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,760
You dare call me a loser?

73
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:28,200
I hate it when people call me that.

74
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:33,840
Then let me show you
what I'm capable of!

75
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,600
You've got some nerve.

76
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:52,040
Today, I'll teach you a lesson.

77
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,200
If you're going to fight,
take it outside.

78
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,040
Get out, both of you!

79
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,120
Qiao Xiaomi,

80
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,280
is that any way to talk to your brother?

81
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,040
Show some respect.

82
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,080
No need to thank me.

83
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,920
Qiao Zhiwei,

84
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:40,120
listen carefully.

85
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,480
Starting today,

86
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,960
I'm the one in charge
of this family.

87
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,720
So you'd better learn

88
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,640
how a dog wags its tail.

89
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,520
Otherwise,

90
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:55,640
I don't mind leaving you with nothing.

91
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,760
Do you understand?

92
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,960
Let...

93
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,600
Let go of me first.

94
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,280
Fine.

95
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,960
As your brother,

96
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,600
I won't stoop to your level.

97
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,640
Enjoyed the show?

98
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,320
Three years apart,

99
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,880
and now you've learned
to train dogs too.

100
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,600
Then why are you still here? Get lost.

101
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:41,680
The thing is, this dog

102
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,360
doesn't train easily.

103
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,440
But

104
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,280
I do have my good points.

105
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,200
I'm loyal.

106
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,080
Don't you want to know
what you've forgotten?

107
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,520
Drink this tea,

108
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,480
and leave.

109
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,680
The day your father forced us apart,

110
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,960
we were both heartbroken.

111
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,600
But I promised you

112
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,240
that I'd come back for you.

113
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:22,680
It's been three years.

114
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,960
I've missed you every single day.

115
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,000
How touching.

116
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,560
But I don't believe you.

117
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,160
Why not?

118
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:40,160
Because my father wasn't
the man you claim he was.

119
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:41,640
He was barely laid to rest.

120
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:44,520
If you say one more thing
against him,

121
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,080
I really won't go easy on you.

122
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,920
That's okay!

123
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,400
I'll help you recover
your memories, little by little!

124
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,800
What a performance.

125
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,120
Keep it up.

126
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,720
Don't worry about me.

127
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,280
There's a role I'd like you to play.

128
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,520
Not sure if you're interested.

129
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:34,820
(July 7, 2022) (Every time
I dream of that fire, there's a girl...)

130
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:38,860
(March 26, 2024)
(Memories have an easel.)

131
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,280
What exactly

132
00:09:40,920 --> 00:09:42,040
happened three years ago?

133
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:44,920
I'm Qin Yu.

134
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,600
I've come back to marry you.

135
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,840
I'm your fiancé.

136
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,240
It's been three years.

137
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,480
I've missed you every single day.

138
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,040
That's okay!

139
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:58,360
I'll help you recover
your memories, little by little!

140
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,800
Is Qin Yu really my fiancé?

141
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:04,410
(Qin Yu... My fiancé?)

142
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,480
(Qin Yu... My fiancé?)
Why did he choose to come back now?

143
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:08,520
Dad,

144
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,040
for the past three years,

145
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,640
you never allowed me

146
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:13,440
to bring up anything
related to the fire.

147
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:16,880
But I've never stopped
trying to recover my memories.

148
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,320
Don't worry.

149
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,360
I'll protect this family,

150
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,480
and find my true self.

151
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:41,080
I've waited three years.

152
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,840
This show is finally about to begin.

153
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:16,930
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

154
00:11:16,930 --> 00:11:20,350
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

155
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:23,840
♪The sweeter it is,
the luckier we seem♪

156
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:27,830
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

157
00:11:29,070 --> 00:11:30,930
♪Let me go, set me free♪

158
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:34,970
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

159
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:40,920
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

160
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:44,410
♪The freedom you gave me♪

161
00:11:44,410 --> 00:11:48,050
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

162
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:51,580
♪Love can barely move forward♪

163
00:11:51,580 --> 00:11:55,360
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

164
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,700
♪The closeness I long for♪

165
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:03,090
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

166
00:12:03,500 --> 00:12:05,320
♪I don't want to break free♪

167
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:10,690
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

